source.name: Food Hubs
source.description: This is a list of food hubs that USDA's Agricultural Marketing Service had on record as of January 2013.  By offering a combination of production, aggregation, distribution, and marketing services, food hubs make it possible for producers to gain entry into new and additional markets that would be difficult or impossible to access on their own.
